title: Body of missing German tourist found in Central Australia: police
text:
Body of missing German tourist Gisela Thor found in Central Australia, police say Posted February 14, 2017 18:11:35 
Northern Territory Police have found a woman's body at Trephina Gorge, east of Alice Springs, believed to be missing German woman Gisela Thor. 
The discovery comes one day after her 76-year-old husband's body was also found. 
More to come.
